description:
See them Live in Augusta! Late Show added! bit.ly/augustLatenight On this very special episode of The 85 South Show the coldest podcast returns to the comedy club scene and plays The LOL Comedy club in San Antonio! Big Gurl steals the show and showcases her confidence, DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller and Chico Bean roast everybody in the small club and somebody proposes in the front row. This episode is all about love!
